
<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Who is Stephan Brown?</h1>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag 'about_me_pic.jpg', width: 300, alt: 'profile image', class: 'profile-img' %>
    
      <div class="skills">
        <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
        <div>
          <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
        <div class="progress">
          <div 
             class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
             role="progressbar"
             aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
             aria-valuemax="100"
             style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
             ></div>
          </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <p>Formerly a J2EE Backend Developer, i am currently a Ruby on Rails Web Developer who specialized in web development specifically with Rails 5, as well as Bootstrap and Ajax.
      A huge fan of learning new frameworks and technologies to where i'm currently in the process of Angular 2 development and generating exciting new applications. Feel free to visit
      my portfolio page to access the latest apps i have created as well as my blog page where i make weekly blog posts related to my development career.</p>
 

    <p>
      <button
        class="btn btn-primary"
        type="button"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#jobHistory"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controler="#jobHistory"
        >Job History
        </button>
              <button
        class="btn btn-warning"
        type="button"
        data-toggle="collapse"
        data-target="#education"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controler="#education"
        >Education
        </button>
        
    </p>

    <p>
      <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
        <div class="card card-block">
          Bartech Systems International
            Web Developer
        </div>
        <div class="card card-block">
          Rei Systems
           Associate Software Developer
        </div>
        <div class="card card-block">
          Telos Inc
           Software Developer
        </div>
        <div class="card card-block">
          Office of Personnel Management
           Software Developer
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="collapse" id="education">
        <div class="card card-block">
          Radford University, Bachelors of Science - Information Systems
        </div>
      </div>
    </p>

   </div>
</div>
  </div>
</div>




